description: Workers set about making the construction site in Paris compatible with social distance rules.
title: Coronavirus: Notre-Dame repairs restart amid lockdown

maintext: "When that's removed, we can say that the phase of making safe will have been completed," he reportedly said, adding that despite losing six weeks the restoration project was still on track to meet President Macron's deadline.
